WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.120
So today I'll be presenting some data on our Phase 2 study of oral Dacitabine plus Venetoclax

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.200
as a fully oral option for AML.

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:13.080
So as we know, acute myeloid leukemia is predominantly a disease of older adults.

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:17.900
These patients are challenging to treat because they have a higher comorbidity burden, lower

00:00:17.900 --> 00:00:22.960
physiological reserve, and also have a higher incidence of adverse risk AML genetics.

00:00:23.580 --> 00:00:28.060
And they may not be candidates for intensive chemotherapy or allergenic stem cell transplantation.

00:00:28.260 --> 00:00:34.140
The Phase 3 Viali-A study established Aza-Venetoclax as the standard of care in this patient population.

00:00:35.140 --> 00:00:41.280
ASTX-727 is an oral formulation of Dacitabine with pharmacokinetic AUC exposure equivalent

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:42.300
to IV Dacitabine.

00:00:42.740 --> 00:00:46.900
So this now allows a fully oral HMA-VEN combination for AML.

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:51.000
So this was a Phase 2 study looking at that, and there's both a frontline arm and a relapsed

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:52.320
refractory arm in this study.

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:55.060
These are the eligibility criteria.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:58.180
This was a study for patients.

00:00:58.260 --> 00:00:59.560
This is a study of AML over age 18.

00:01:00.120 --> 00:01:05.780
In the frontline or older unfit cohort, patients needed to be either age 75 or above or have

00:01:05.780 --> 00:01:08.700
a major comorbidity, including intensive chemotherapy.

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.040
The primary objective was overall response rate.

00:01:12.700 --> 00:01:16.680
Secondary objectives were overall survival, relapse-free survival, duration of response,

00:01:16.740 --> 00:01:17.220
and safety.

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:20.480
This is a treatment plan.

00:01:20.620 --> 00:01:23.860
So the treatment was given in 28-day cycles, up to 24 cycles.

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:27.500
Induction was five days of ASTX-727.

00:01:27.500 --> 00:01:27.600
And this was a study of AML over age 18.

