00:01:28.260 --> 00:01:33.920
And venetoclax was given with a three-day ramp-up, then up until day 28.

00:01:34.020 --> 00:01:38.480
However, the venetoclax could be held at day 21 based on an early bone marrow if the blast

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:38.920
had cleared.

00:01:39.480 --> 00:01:43.640
And the dose of venetoclax was adjusted for concomitant CYP384 inhibitors.

00:01:44.940 --> 00:01:50.880
Consolidation was five days of ASTX-727 and 21 days of venetoclax, although the doses

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:56.220
were permitted to be reduced to three days for ASTX and 14 days for venetoclax in patients

00:01:56.220 --> 00:01:58.240
where there was a concern for myelosuppression or toxin.

